TopicTitle: Jeb refueses to use his piloting skills.

Articles.Content:
Hi.

Not only Jeb, but all pilots only make use of their "stay on course"-skill. But the others like retro, pro...etc. don't work.

I think there might be some mod interfering. Someone has an idea?

Is this happening in sandbox or career?In career,pilot have to get some experience points to be able to use other "SAS" function.Only 5 star pilot can use all the functions.
I've had this problem, and I'm fairly sure it's to do with the FieldExperience mod. Reloading usually fixes it.
